00:00:00.850 --> 00:00:05.290
just like you have a relationship with those that are below you, the ones

00:00:05.290 --> 00:00:09.720
 above you should be similar. It should be a relationship of consistency,

00:00:09.720 --> 00:00:14.160
 of respect, of the position. Even if you disagree with the

00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:18.600
 personality or the circumstance of the person in front of you are, uh,

00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:23.030
 immediately above you, you need to respect the position you need

00:00:23.030 --> 00:00:27.470
 to understand that they were placed there for such a time. Is that And

00:00:27.470 --> 00:00:31.910
 also you need to figure out is what do I need to do to meet the needs

00:00:31.910 --> 00:00:36.340
 of this individual? How do I take care of them? How do I make them

00:00:36.340 --> 00:00:40.780
 a better leader from my position?

